### Component 3: Database Schema & TypeORM Entities

All 20+ tables from the Architecture Document Section 5, implemented as TypeORM entities with proper relationships, indexes, and constraints.

#### Entity Files (each in `apps/api/src/database/entities/`)

| Entity File | Table | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| `user.entity.ts` | `users` | UUID PK, role enum, status enum, email unique index, bcrypt hash |
| `seeker-profile.entity.ts` | `seeker_profiles` | 1:1 with users, CASCADE delete, TEXT[] skills array |
| `employer-profile.entity.ts` | `employer_profiles` | 1:1 with users, JSONB social_links |
| `job.entity.ts` | `jobs` | Full-text index on title+description, 6 enums, employer FK |
| `application.entity.ts` | `applications` | UNIQUE(job_id, seeker_id), status pipeline enum |
| `saved-job.entity.ts` | `saved_jobs` | UNIQUE(job_id, seeker_id) |
| `company-review.entity.ts` | `company_reviews` | 5 rating dimensions, submitter_hash, nullable user_id |
| `salary-review.entity.ts` | `salary_reviews` | No user_id (anonymous), NUMERIC(12,2), period enum |
| `shop-product.entity.ts` | `shop_products` | listing_type + pricing_type enums, S3 key (never exposed) |
| `order.entity.ts` | `orders` | 7-state status enum, commission/earnings split, escrow timestamps |
| `quote-request.entity.ts` | `quote_requests` | 5-state status, 7-day expiry, checkout_link flag |
| `order-dispute.entity.ts` | `order_disputes` | UNIQUE on order_id, evidence_urls TEXT[], resolution tracking |
| `post.entity.ts` | `posts` | Denormalized likes/comments count |
| `post-like.entity.ts` | `post_likes` | UNIQUE(post_id, user_id) |
| `post-comment.entity.ts` | `post_comments` | author FK, body TEXT |
| `follow.entity.ts` | `follows` | UNIQUE(follower_id, followee_id), status enum |
| `message.entity.ts` | `messages` | Composite index (sender, receiver), read_at nullable |
| `report.entity.ts` | `reports` | Polymorphic: target_type enum + target_id UUID |
| `email-verification.entity.ts` | `email_verifications` | 24h expiry, used_at tracking |
| `password-reset.entity.ts` | `password_resets` | 1h expiry, used_at tracking |
| `notification.entity.ts` | `notifications` | type, message, is_read, link |
| `legal-page.entity.ts` | `legal_pages` | slug unique, WYSIWYG content, updated_by FK |
| `ad.entity.ts` | `ads` | type enum, placement, date range, status |
| `newsletter-send.entity.ts` | `newsletter_sends` | audience enum, recipient_count |
| `product-rating.entity.ts` | `product_ratings` | UNIQUE(product_id, buyer_id), verified buyers only |
| `seller-application.entity.ts` | `seller_applications` | status enum, reviewed_by FK |

#### [NEW] Initial Migration
- Auto-generated from entities via `typeorm migration:generate`
- Includes all indexes: email, company_name, industry, role, full-text on jobs
- All ENUM types created as PostgreSQL custom types
- All UNIQUE constraints and foreign keys with CASCADE rules

